    },
    "The gateless gate has been open all along" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Das torlose Tor war die ganze Zeit offen"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The goal of this app is to not need it anymore.\nUntil then: Breathe." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Das Ziel dieser App ist, dass Du sie nicht mehr brauchst.\nBis dahin: Atme."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The journey of awareness has no finish line" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Die Reise der Achtsamkeit hat keine Ziellinie"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The monkey mind wins today's round — tomorrow is yours" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Der Affengeist gewinnt die heutige Runde — morgen gehört dir"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The river flows as it always has" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Der Fluss fließt wie eh und je"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The wheel turns. You are the axle." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Das Rad dreht sich. Du bist die Achse."
          }
        }
